<span id="freeTextContainer7364146049938102827">Basically this is a story about a 7 year-old girl who goes missing. Some chapters are from the perspective of each of the parents, some are from the POV of the (ghost?) girl, and other chapters are stories of maybe people tangentially related, or perhaps unrelated to the rest of the narrative. It&apos;s about grief of course, and sometimes in a fantastical form.</span>
